'''eIF1'''（eukaryotic initiation factor 1，[[真核起始因子|真核起始因子]]1）是一种参与[[真核翻译|真核翻译]]起始的重要的[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]。eIF1在[[密码子|起始密码子]]AUG的识别中发挥重要的作用，它能使起始密码子的识别具有很高的保真度。

在[[酵母|酵母]]中，eIF1是维持其生存不可或缺的蛋白质。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Yoon H and Donahue TF|year=1992|title= The sui1 supressor locus in Saccharomyces cerevisiae encodes a translation factor that functions during tRNA<sub>i</sub><sup>Met</sup> recognition of the start codon|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_molecular-and-cellular-biology_1992-01_12_1/page/248|journal= Mol Cell Biol|volume= 12|pages= 248–260}}</ref>

== 功能机制 ==
eIF1结合在40S[[核糖体|核糖体]]亚基的表面，可能影响在48前起始复合物中40S亚基的表面构象及[[mRNA|mRNA]]和Met-[[tRNA|tRNA]]<sub>i</sub>的结合位置。在[[密码子|密码子]]与[[反密码子|反密码子]]没有正确配对时，eIF1可以抑制[[GTP|GTP]]的水解，当密码子的识别完成后，eIF1的抑制作用被减弱，并且实验发现eIF1的抑制作用的减弱需要精确的AUG的配对，而其它例如UUG或CAA的识别并没有类似功能。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Unbehaun, A., Borukhov, S. I., Hellen, C. U. & Pestova, T. V.|title=Release of initiation factors from 48S complexes during ribosomal subunit joining and the link between establishment of codon-anticodon base-pairing and hydrolysis of eIF2-bound GTP|journal= Genes Dev|volume=18|pages= 3078-93 |year=2004}}</ref>

== 结构 ==
eIF1[[蛋白质|结构]]属于α+β型折叠，包含了一个由5个β链组成的[[β折叠|β折叠]]片和两个[[α螺旋|α螺旋]]组成的[[结构域|结构域]]，其[[N末端|N末端]]为一段较长的无结构区域。<ref>{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Fletcher CM, Pestova TV, Hellen CU, Wagner G|title=Structure and interactions of the translation initiation factor eIF1|journal=EMBO J|volume=18|year=1999|pages=2631-7|pmid=10228174}}</ref><ref name="yeast structure">{{en}}{{cite journal en|author=Reibarkh M, Yamamoto Y, Singh CR, del Rio F, Fahmy A, Lee B, Luna RE, Ii M, Wagner G, Asano K|title=Eukaryotic initiation factor (eIF) 1 carries two distinct eIF5-binding faces important for multifactor assembly and AUG selection|journal=J Biol Chem|volume=283|year=2007|pages=1094-103|pmid=17974565}}</ref>eIF1被发现能够以不同的蛋白质表面与40S核糖体亚基以及[[eIF2|eIF2]]、[[eIF3|eIF3]]和[[eIF5|eIF5]]结合。<ref name="yeast structure"/>

